  "texts": [
    "A three-step process is described by Charalambous et al. [10] for addressing automotive vulnerability issues.",
    "Bounded Model Checking (BMC) is the first step in the process.",
    "It evaluates the user-provided source code to a property specification.",
    "The original code and the appropriate counterexample are provided to the LLM module by the BMC engine in the scenario that this phase's verification is unsuccessful and a security property violation is detected.",
    "Secondly, customized queries are sent to the LLM engine to produce a corrected version of the code."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "A three-step process is described by Charalambous et al. [10] for addressing automotive vulnerability issues."
  ]
}